    <h1><span class="marker">&#x25BC;</span> May 3, 2007 Newsletter</h1>
    <img src="../graphics/blue_linefade395.jpg" width="395" alt="" />

    <div class="author">Stuart Cooper, GSMM campaign manager</div>

    <p>In this issue:</p>
    
